DESCRIPTION:$8.00 - Tickets for the 8 PM screening of THE MOMENT 2025 • 
 USA • 103 minutes • dir. Aidan Zamiri Wednesday\, April 1st at The Bac
 k Door (207 S College Ave) $8 | 21+ Showtime: 8 pm TRAILER Synopsis : Chan
 neling both This is Spinal Tap (1984) and Spice World (1997)\, Charli XCX'
 s The Moment is a playful\, hilarious\, self-critical mockumentary about t
 he iconic pop star and the price of fame. Co-starring Alexander Skarsgård
  and Hailey Gates\, as well as numerous cameos\, Charli XCX plays a versio
 n of herself as she embarks on a worldwide tour in support of the album br
 at\, navigating studio pressure\, corporate sponsorship\, and fan expectat
 ions. Can she survive The Moment with her cultural legacy intact? Find out
  with a very special April Fool's Day screening\, Wednesday\, April 1\, at
  the Back Door! (we promise this is not a prank)
